{"id":"knead","term":"Knead","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>To prepare dough in the process of baking (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 18:6\">Gen. 18:6</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Samuel 28:24\">1 Sam. 28:24</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Hosea 7:4\">Hos. 7:4</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Genesis 18:6","1 Samuel 28:24","Hosea 7:4"]}